scripts.build-dev: dart pub get && dart compile js -O2 -o build/main.dart.js web/main.dart --define=include.debug.utils=false
scripts.build-prod: dart pub get && dart compile js -O4 -o build/main.dart.js web/main.dart --define=include.debug.utils=false --define=jaspr.web.debug=false --define=jaspr.flags.verbose=false
